{"tid":601124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"溫州「櫻花海洋」造假　購票市民入場驚見全場膠花","createTime":"2018-03-22T03:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T04:01:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0b523f81754a841c713464394bfc4ff4a3706881","tid":601124,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180322/s00004/f4ebd20ebfe7697d3f01706a9752a191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180322%2Fs00004%2Ff4ebd20ebfe7697d3f01706a9752a191.jpg&h=ecba1e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上不少人戲稱，在中國，只有賊人是真的。內地傳媒報道，溫州一個主辦單位大搞「櫻花海洋」、「櫻花大道」，吸引遊人購票入場，惟最終買票入場者竟然發現，所說的「櫻花」全是塑膠花，被揭發後大會辯稱，真花變膠花是因為櫻花在運送途中凋謝了，故只能以假花代替。<br />\n<br />\n據報大會安排了逾百株假花到場，而至今共出售逾百張門票，獲利數千元。<br />\n<br />\n興沖沖賞花卻花錢看膠花，消費者大感不滿紛作投訴，據了解當地市場監督管理局介入事件，要求主辦單位退款，並對疑虛假宣傳的涉事單位及場地提供者展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180322/s00004/1521688549293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180322%2Fs00004%2F1521688549293&d=p9Oj975Ubuqw252xh3w5LpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=17bc6ba0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180322%2Fs00004%2F1521688549293&h=4154a876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180322/s00004/1521688549293</a>"},{"pid":"2b808f0ad63b2199e44d164ed30076c998cd9b8f","tid":601124,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"上次叫雞中假波雞<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c664d6ece769d8390daebf1caaa8250b04adc6fe","tid":601124,"uid":22959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"真花咪又係唔夠一星期就俾d 蝗折斷曬d 枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9776ddac89602c9c07233ee36cb251e1a864b5d","tid":601124,"uid":174191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:32:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">被揭發後大會辯稱，真花變膠花是因為櫻花在運送途中凋謝了，故只能以假花代替</span><br />\n<br />\n你係有心嘅就成個活動取消而唔係攞假花嚟呃鳩人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n運送嗰陣謝咗喎，邊個會信啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df601d16c03406bb002500bb2801a9510fc627fe","tid":601124,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c664d6ece769d8390daebf1caaa8250b04adc6fe","tid":601124,"uid":22959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"真花咪又係唔夠一星期就俾d 蝗折斷曬d 枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"符合蝗情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2571d4aa9c3c22242bc69df561166b8c2a25504","tid":601124,"uid":60333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"中國得騙子係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c71c78d7957c9d310c2efe3506adb584032b102","tid":601124,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"用假銀紙買假門要睇假桜花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863dff3cbcc2ae098ad40844c46f28cceaba9f83","tid":601124,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"真花會比支那蟲搣走晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647f1991252b04f986c4dc32857dde6496601251","tid":601124,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c664d6ece769d8390da